  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Recognition of professional qualifications: guidance for regulatory bodies
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  

  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    Guidance explaining how the recognition of professional qualifications will operate if we leave the EU without a deal.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

